$NetBSD: patch-aa,v 1.3 2012/09/21 11:46:56 ryoon Exp $

Adapt ls(1) arguments for BSD.
Do not install man page gzipped.
Do not install into /usr.
Add case for NetBSD and DragonFly in the wrapper script.

